org.eclipse.scada.configuration.globalization

Interface Local

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalImpl

    public interface Local
    A representation of the model object 'Local'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Local
    • Logon Credentials
    • Filters
    • Default Include
    • Global
    • Authoratives
    • Id

    See Also:
    GlobalizePackage.getLocal()
